  <brief_title>Colchicine in Coronary Artery Bypass Graft (CABG)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Study of Anti-inflammatory Treatment With Colchicine in Patients Undergoing Elective Coronary Artery Bypass Graft Surgery to Reduce Reperfusion Damage</official_title>
